text: British Somaliland, officially the Somaliland Protectorate (), was a British protectorate in present-day Somaliland. The territory was bordered by Darawiish, Italian Somaliland, French Somaliland and Abyssinia. From 1940 to 1941, it was occupied by the Italians and was part of Italian East Africa. ==References== Category:1884 establishments in Africa Category:1960 disestablishments in Africa Category:Former British colonies Category:Former colonies in Africa Category:History of Somalia
